name: Fetch Commit Project Branch Daily
script:
commit_branches_daily = frappe.get_list("Commit Project Branch", filters={"frequency": "Daily"}, pluck='name')

for branch in commit_branches_daily :
    branch_doc = frappe.get_doc("Commit Project Branch", branch)
    branch_doc.fetch_repo()
    branch_doc.save()
    
frappe.db.commit()
